Examples of JQLs: 
project = DMC and issueType in (epic) - get list of epics
project = DMC and issueType in (story) and parent in (DMC-100) - get all stories inside epic
project = DMC and issueType in (subtask) and parent in (DMC-300) - get all subtasks inside story
project = DMC and issueType in (bug) and parent in (DMC-100) - get all bugs inside epic

